Package common

Class TestData

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.TestData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class TestData
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The TestData class represents the data for a test. It contains information such as the test ID, course, date, time allocated, number of students started, number of submissions, number of not submitted, average score, median score, score distribution, and author. The class implements the Serializable interface to support object serialization.
